body: "GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/488\\n\\nDuplicate evidence: exact all-status searches for GH-488 and path-target init follow-up commands returned no canonical item. Related historical pm-jek2 fixed caller-settings corruption, not generated next-step correctness. This item owns executable result/recovery guidance and an explicit workspace-target primitive."
